      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like i'm taking up space that i don't even need anymore. they have so much on their plates, and instead of being able to enjoy them, i'm just a problem they have to solve every week. i look at them and i just... i want them to be free of me. i want them to have their lives back without worrying about my next appointment or my next fall. wouldn't it be better if it just ended? if i just wasn't there to weigh them down?",
